---

<BaseLayout>
  <h1>Typography Foundation</h1>
  <p>
    This is a demonstration of the typography foundation. The text should render in
    Source Serif 4 at 18px with a line-height of 1.65. The color should be #111 on
    a white background.
  </p>
  <p>
    The content column has a maximum width of 680px, is centered with auto margins,
    and has horizontal padding of 1.5rem (24px) for comfortable mobile reading.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
